description: Eric Johnson with Kyle Brock and Tommy Taylor performing "Cliffs Of Dover" on December 14th, 1988 . This performance is available on the New West records CD and DVD entitled "Eric Johnson Live from Austin Texas". Original studio version is available on the Capitol Records CD entitled "Ah Via Musicom".
